frameDefinitions: These words refer to separating a Whole into Parts, or separating one part from another.
An individual or group (Practitioner) or a part of their work life (Work) is defined professionally by the Activity that they typically engage in.
An Object with an understood function is or is not in a state ready to perform that function.
There is a certain physical Distance within which some other entity can participate in an Event (typically perception or manipulation) with the Participant.
A Group is described as having members which are similar or dissimilar to each other.
An Entity is at a particular stage of its development.
